{"tid":1909822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACK PINK傳與Lady GaGa合作：暫時好難透露","createTime":"2020-03-04T08:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T13:48:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"110d0f5338e4567a774cbf015928d594797a9d42","tid":1909822,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"美國天后Lady GaGa將於下月推出新碟，今日有英國媒體指有傳當中有新歌是與韓國女團BLACK PINK及美國小天后Ariana Grande合作。<br />\n<br />\n據指傳聞是從GaGa的有關人士口中聽到，現時英國的著名音樂評論網站的相關人士亦聽過她們合作的傳聞，而最近GaGa追蹤了BLACK PINK的官方社交網帳號，GaGa的御用製作人亦關注了BLACK PINK成員Jisoo及Rose的帳號。<br />\n<br />\n對於被指會與GaGa合作，BLACK PINK所屬的YG事務所表示：「現在這一刻很難告知大家，為了等待那麼久的粉絲，我們將會以好的音樂和消息報答大家。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200304/bkn-20200304160952342-0304_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200304%2Fbkn-20200304160952342-0304_00862_001.html&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=5363bb41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200304/bkn-20200304160952342-0304_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"71321399815c684bc6e6ef6fc26087b3e2567a59","tid":1909822,"uid":191633,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"咁即係阿Rose幾時solo"},{"pid":"2caaee98c4e7daf61ff6ebfaadad503be9801b7c","tid":1909822,"uid":165368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"證明我bp勁到休息緊都有人R合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25159eb43b72792b5a76b874ba5c469aac6638d7","tid":1909822,"uid":52073,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2caaee98c4e7daf61ff6ebfaadad503be9801b7c","tid":1909822,"uid":165368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"證明我bp勁到休息緊都有人R合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj